# 🛠 DroidWatch AI — Prototype & Implementation Plan

## Prototype Overview

DroidWatch AI is an **AI-powered Android Cyber Attack & Defense Simulation Platform** designed to safely execute suspicious Android APKs inside an isolated sandbox environment and dynamically reconstruct malware behavior.

The prototype demonstrates:

- Safe APK execution
- Runtime behavioral monitoring
- Multi-layer attack analysis
- Adaptive defense simulation
- AI-assisted threat intelligence
- Interactive visualization dashboard

